Currently, the Customers view is a large list of everyone who is able to submit tickets to a particular service desk. In some instances, this includes a grouping of both internal jira-users, as well as external third party customers with portal access only. As an administrator, I think it would be valuable to be able to filter out jira-users and others with application access so that only portal customers are visible. In a very large list of customers on a larger service desk, it would be incredibly useful to be able to see only the external users with access.

